Lastly, it‚Äôs the classic AE86. Powered by a 1.6-litre 4-cylinder engine, the power output is well down on the two other competitors, at 124hp and 145Nm. title: Russia warns of missile strike on World Court after German Minister vows to arrest Putin
description:
Russia has warned of a hypersonic missile strike on the International Criminal Court in The Hague over its arrest warrant against President Vladimir Putin. The threat came hours after German Justice Minister said that the NATO nation can arrest Vladimir Putin if he dares to step on its territory. "Gentlemen, everyone walks under God and missiles. It is quite possible to imagine the targeted use of hypersonic Oniks from the North Sea by a Russian ship at The Hague court building. Unfortunately, it cannot be shot down. And the court is just a poor international organisation, not the population of a NATO country. That's why they won't start a war," wrote former Russian President Dmitry Medvedev on Telegram.

title: Purple Cabbages added more colour to already colourful dishes! Bro made pickles too | Traditional Me
description:
Our elder aunt's husband hails from the Sri Lankan hill country town of Welimada. All his relatives are from Nuwara Eliya ( The most picturesque and coldest mountainous city that is surrounded by lush green mountains and high cold waterfalls, in Sri Lanka). When we were young, we used to like visiting Nuwara Eliya due to the hot weather in our hamlet of Dankotuwa. I suppose primarily because Nuwara Eliya's ice-cold weather and daylong mist-covered city, made for a very enjoyable experience for us. Elder uncle made Dankotuwa his second home because there is plenty of land for vegetable farming. The elder uncle's relatives from Nuwara Eliya visit their home in Dankotuwa once or twice a year. They always bring fresh vegetables that are cultivated exclusively in Nuwara-Eliya like Purple cabbage, Red turnip, Broccoli, Cauliflower, Rhubarb, Broad beans, Lettuce, Kale leaves and so and so, when they visit our uncle and his family because those vegetables are not typical and are not grown in our village due to climatic conditions. They came to see our aunt and uncle again this year ahead of the Sri Lankan new year.

Our brother always hangs out with the Nuwara Eliya crowd when they visit. Every time they bring vegetables to our aunt and uncle, they also send us half of those same vegetables. But this time, things were a little odd because our brother had just brought only Purple cabbage from our aunt's house. I inquired about the purple cabbages out of curiosity, and he replied that he is going to make a salad for our aunt and family too. To prepare that salad, the cabbage must first be pickled by immersed in water that has been boiled with vinegar, salt and the required spices. I used to get one or two cabbages from the store on other days and make this salad. But this time there were lots of cabbages. Along with beetroots, brother had also created another version of a pickle. Since my brother did the pickling part, I only had to make the salad. For a little twist I added pineapples and fried dates and blackcurrants to give it more flavours and colours,

I prepared rice for lunch in the afternoon by combining purple cabbage. I used the juice from butterfly pea flowers (nil-katarolu) to colour the rice blue. The combination of white and blue rice pearls was stunning and vibrant. The purple cabbage chunks significantly improved both the colour and flavour of this unusual rice. I prepared fish red curry, tempered dhal curry and tomato salad as side dishes. Actually, colourfulness and great taste are always a must at any lunch or dinner table. Those colours bring pleasing tastes to the eyes as well-incorporated spices enhance any curry in the art of cooking.

Love you All!
Nadee

Mexico took on Japan in the semifinals of the 2023 World Baseball Classic. Mexico's Luis Urias hit a three-run home run in the fourth inning to give Mexico a 3-0 lead. Mexico quickly responded with Alex Verdugo's RBI double and Isaac Paredes' RBI single, to put Mexico ahead 5-3 in the top of the eighth inning. Japan's Hotaka Yamakawa hit a sacrifice fly to bring Japan within one in the bottom of the eighth, 5-4. Finally, in the bottom of the ninth Munetaka Murakami hit a two-run double to give Japan a 6-5 walk-off win over Mexico. This instant WBC classic sent Japan to the championship against USA.

title: Should India HELP Pakistan? | Pakistan Economic Crisis
description:
Pakistan, as we know, is facing an unprecedented economic crisis. The prices of food have sky rocketed, malls and offices are being shut down and people are being advised to drink less tea so that the government can save money! Some people are even saying that India should help Pakistan out. 
In the midst of all of this, the Pakistani PM has called for making peace with India. 
He says that after three wars, Pakistan has learnt its lesson. 
But this is not the first time Pakistan has been talking about peace. Several attempts to establish peace have been made in the past.
But peace has been elusive so far.
So, could this time be different? Should India help Pakistan? Would that buy us peace in return?
This is what we are going to talk about in this video. We also discuss why our previous attempts of peace with Pakistan have failed and why this time the situation could be different, if India decides to help at all.

title: MANDALORIAN Season 3 Episode 4 BREAKDOWN - Jar-Jar saved Grogu + Star Wars Easter Eggs
description:
Our MANDALORIAN Season 3 Episode 4 Breakdown is here! Thanks to Cufflinks for sponsoring this video! Use code SCREENCRUSH20 will get you 20% SITEWIDE through May the 4th. https://www.cufflinks.com/

Get Your Doug Foundling and Palpatine Returns Shirts Here ‚Üí http://shopzeroedition.com/collections/screen-crush-merch

Go here ‚Üí http://screencrush.com/

Follow us ‚Üí https://twitter.com/screencrushnews
Get our newsletter ‚Üí http://screencrush.com/newsletter/

Written and Hosted by Ryan Arey (http://twitter.com/ryanarey)
Edited by Harriet Lengel-Enright, Randolf Nombrado, Brianna McLarty, and Colton Ogburn

#Mandalorian #EasterEggs #JarJarRedeemed 

The helmets at the intro go by pretty fast so in case you missed them we have darth vader in sith red, R2-D2, Fennec shand, a TIE pilot, bo katan, IG-11, a scout trooper, and a mandalorian. In the past I said this last one was din, but [I was wrong]. You can see some scratches on the helmet that dosn;t match din‚Äôs. Also, each of the bad guys in the opening is red, the good guys are blue. So whoever this mystery mandalorian is, he‚Äôs a bad guy.

So welcome to the closest we‚Äôll get to a beach episode of the mandalorian.


Doug: What;s a beach episode?
Well, as Screenrush‚Äôs Srinidhi Rao tells me, a beach episode is a TV trope, common in anime, where the cast spends the episode relaxing on a beach. Sometimes it's an excuse to see the cats in swimsuits, but it‚Äôs usually important for character building. When we see heroes with their guard down, they get closer to each other, and by extension the audience. IN a way, the Ultron after party is a beach episode that doens;t even take place on a beach [clip].

So this episode is very similar‚Äìand not just because they‚Äôre on a beach. I doesn;t do much to further the overall story of Din, Grogu, or the new republic. But it does give us a chase to see the heroes in a relaxing setting, as they contemplate their place in the world. Bo Katan is finding her way in the new covert, while grogu is reckoning with the trauma of his past. 

So we open in the covert training, and Bo Katan is very much the protagonist of this episode. She is the first POV character we follow around, as she watches them all train. And it makes sense for her to be our POV character, because‚Äìlike her‚Äìthis is all new for us. 

The mandalorians are all training in pretty typical combat we‚Äôve seen before. There's a practice dummy on the shore. We see spears. Vobro blades like we saw din and paz sue on each other in chapter 3, dueling flame throwers, and then they‚Äôre all kind of hilariously shooting into the water for no reason. I mean, that‚Äôs not really the target practice that‚Äôs killing time.

In fact this scene with all of them training seems to mirror a similar scene in the clone wars, where Pre-Vizsla tours the mandalorian camp with a newly-revived Darth maul.

Now one thing that‚Äôs interesting about bo katan‚Äìshe was a member of death watch. During the clone wars, the mandalorians were mostly pascificts, and they were led by her sister, Duchess satine. But Bo Katan was part of a group called death watch‚Äìthey were violent armor-wearing mandalorians who lived on the same moon that din is from. 

Death watch believed the traditional ways of the mandalorian‚Äìlike wearing armor and combat and this group‚Äìthe children of the watch‚Äìare an even more extreme cult who believe you should never remove your helmet at all. So Bo-Katan was trained to be a fighter, she‚Äôs familiar with these exercises and traditions. But It's still a bit of a culture shock for her. I would like to see a flashback explaining why she broke with ehr family and joined a terrorist group on the moon. 

She did mention that her dad was a fighter, so maybe it was actually her sister Saine who was the one who broke from the family way and became a pacifist. 

Cufflinks ad here

So cufflinks has a special discount for ScreenCrush fans. If you use the code Screen Crush 20, you get 20% off any item site wide. Back to the easter eggs. 

So while the mandalorian kids are training in their combat, it looks like grogu is doing jedi training, getting ready to move rocks with his mind. [last jedi, more than moving rocks]. But it turns out that they were actually crabs and that he was just being distracted by food. There‚Äôs a bit of parallel here to the main storyline. Both the flashback and present day story are about predators and prey. The clone troopers hunt grogu and the jedi, the bat creature hunts the mandalorians, and they end up hunting the creature.

And by the way, one of our writers, Dod Seitz, pointing out the monster seems like an homage to the kaiju Rodan.

Dod also pointed out the similarities to beowulf. Specifically, grenal‚Äôs mom interrupts a banquet, and then beowulf leads his people to the mother‚Äôs den to kill her.

description:
Today AD is welcomed to Columbus, Ohio by Debby Ryan and Josh Dun for a tour of their fascinating, ‚Äòtreehouse fantasy‚Äô home. It might be surprising to hear of a sparkling young actor and her rocker husband setting up their first house in the ‚ÄúArch City,‚Äù but Ryan and¬†Dun relish an impulsive departure from the script. When they discovered the property and decided to make it their home, the actor and musician tapped Fawn Galli and Ashley Moyer to bring their domestic dream to life. From a basement boxing ring and a cold-plunge pool on the back porch, to a recording studio and a dramatic stone bust of Dwayne ‚ÄúThe Rock‚Äù Johnson, that dream has come to full fruition. ‚ÄúI remember walking through the house and feeling like there was so much room to put our personalities into it,‚Äù says Dun. ‚ÄúNot only was this the first house that we designed together, but it was really the first time that both of us felt the freedom to put our mark on a place.‚Äù

title: USA vs. Japan Highlights | 2023 World Baseball Classic Championship
description:
Team USA took on Japan for the 2023 World Baseball Classic Championship. Fireworks started early as Trea Turner hit a solo home run in the second to start the scoring. Munetaka Murakami would answer with a solo home run of his own. Kazuma Okamoto would hit a solo home run of his own in the fourth inning and Japan would take a 3-1 lead. In the 8th inning, Kyle Schwarber gave the USA some hope as he launched a solo home run. Shohei Ohtani would enter in the ninth inning where he would strike out his teammate, Mike Trout to end the game and Japan won the 2023 World Baseball Classic.

title: Counter-Strike 2: Moving Beyond Tick Rate
description:
Tick rate no longer matters for moving, shooting, or throwing.
 
Sub-tick updates are the heart of Counter-Strike 2. Previously, the server only evaluated the world in discrete time intervals (called ticks). Thanks to Counter-Strike 2‚Äôs sub-tick update architecture, servers know the exact instant that motion starts, a shot is fired, or a ‚Äònade is thrown.
 
As a result, regardless of tick rate, your moving and shooting will be equally responsive and your grenades will always land the same way.
